Package: codeAsData
Type: Package
Title: Functions for analysing the code in R packages
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Russ Hyde
Maintainer: Russ Hyde <russ.hyde.data@gmail.com>
Description: This is the supporting R package for an analysis project called `code_as_data`.
    The functions here are used to obtain the source code / git repos for a variety of R packages
    and to analyse the course code therein (lines of code, duplication level and so on).
